com.aurel.track.util.event

Interface IEventSubscriber

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EventHandlerSystemStarted, FieldChangeScriptHandler, FreeMarkerMailHandlerBudgetChange, FreemarkerMailHandlerIssueChange, FreeMarkerMailHandlerReminder

    public interface IEventSubscriber
    This interface describes oberservers that can attach to an AdminEventPublisher. They will get notified of events of administrative actions, like registering of new users etc.
